item.title: We have moved
item.content:encoded:
The Chaostreff Osnabrück e.V. has moved! From now on all meetings will take place in the AStA of the University of Osnabrück, Alte Münze 12, 49074 Osnabrück.

We have given our new Hackspace the name Rabbithole and we look forward to setting up our new home.
item.author: Chaostreff Osnabrück
